 tình yêu. Với thế giới quan trái ngược, tình cảm của họ sẽ nảy nở và phát triển như thế nào?","tmdb":{"type":"tv","id":"233100","season":1,"vote_average":8,"vote_count":52},"modified":"2025-02-15T07:40:09.000Z","cast":["Han Ji-min","Lee Jun-hyuk","Kim Do-hoon","Kim Yoon-hye","Park Bo-kyung","Gi So-you","Lee Sang-hee","Heo Dong-won","Yoon Ga-i","Seo Hye-won","Ko Gun-han","Lee Jae-woo","Song Ji-in","Yun Yoo-sun","Cho Seung-yeon"],"director":["함준호"],"cast_meta":[{"name":"Han Ji-min","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Han Ji-min","tmdb_id":1010877,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/v2c6JPiW2REiElPz5Tlb5LmrLKV.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1010877"},{"name":"Lee Jun-hyuk","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Lee Jun-hyuk","tmdb_id":1254630,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/zXo037qPJhdSvyhAjGCNoT0TcCF.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1254630"},{"name":"Kim Do-hoon","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Kim Do-hoon","tmdb_id":2152558,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/3ISggEbubgBtZiDV7kMVm09X0MG.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2152558"},{"name":"Kim Yoon-hye","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Kim Yoon-hye","tmdb_id":1254557,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/747GCaTzw3owpL85uUTf4FJUWUL.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1254557"},{"name":"Park Bo-kyung","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Park Bo-kyung","tmdb_id":3555452,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/mHM4Zf1Knw6MdPrTsyfzrCckyaV.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/3555452"},{"name":"Gi So-you","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Gi So-you","tmdb_id":3832882,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/h9a5JSuaMpvckOxwIISZ9Of2NOJ.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/3832882"},{"name":"Lee Sang-hee","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Lee Sang-hee","tmdb_id":1374543,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/lf0RoPOizR5YGBolLwWrHj0WQeB.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1374543"},{"name":"Heo